I can tell that there is no sequel to this. Anyway, listen to my story. 
The next day I got a call from my bank telling me an anonymous sender had deposited 42 trillion into my bank, after that fiasco I got a notification on my phone saying the anime Hunter x Hunter and No Game, No Life both got a second season.
I prefer lecia more than sonya :>

Later on in the day I was doing some light exercise when all of a sudden Mike Tyson, Muhammed Ali & Reincarnation Truck came walking/driving through my backyard fence with a bunch of gifts in hand. They told me they were impressed with my exercise routine and offered to train me as their protégée. Teaching me all about boxing form, footwork, power punches. Reincarnation truck bestowed upon me magical powers with infinite magicules so I could do cool stuff like shoot laser beams from my asshole and teleport.
When everyone left after a couple hours later my iPhone 8+ started beeping and flashing, In shock I dropped it but to my surprise it was floating, I’m standing there

dumbfounded when suddenly a gaming interface appears. A voice starts talking 
to me telling me I had been chosen as the next host for the “super system op generator harem king reincarnated god off a million milfs.” And my phone has been transformed into the support centre for the system, an iPhone 1000. It informs me since I’m already op and amazing that the system is maxed out and my abilities are all infinite now. I skim through my abilities and see the “upgrade” button. After reading through the description I point it at my small average house which transforms into a mansion. Same thing with my humble 1996 Toyota Corolla, I press upgrade and it transforms into a 2004 V8 Toyota Corolla with Lexus.
Night time hits, I’m laying down on my billion dollar bed made out of Diamonds and fairy farts. Pretty happy with how the days turned out. I hear a knock on the door, I’m a little weirded out. Regardless I’m OP so I get up and open the door. A modest harem (because I’m loyal) who were made

up of the best 10 milfs of my 1 million milfs. It consisted of 1 demon queen
who is a milf, 5 regular milfs, 3 milf maids and 1 milf elf girl. They all rush into the room onto me and into bed. And an orgy happens and I have a fucking great sleep.
I wake up in the morning to find myself outside in ChickenStore, in the gutter pounding headache and sharp pains in my right leg. Bottle of beer in my left hand and my cleaned out wallet in my right. I get up wobbly, find a dollar in my left pocket then stagger my way over to ChickenStore to get myself a soft serve cone.
